net.truelicense.api

Class UncheckedLicenseManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.truelicense.api.UncheckedLicenseManager

  • public final class UncheckedLicenseManager
extends Object
    Adapts vendor and consumer license managers so that they generally throw an UncheckedLicenseManagementException instead of a (checked) LicenseManagementException if an operation fails.
    Author:
    Christian Schlichtherle
    See Also:
    ConsumerLicenseManager.unchecked(), VendorLicenseManager.unchecked()
